G. verification/

Reality grounding.

reality_checklist.md

Before canonizing a claim:
- Is it testable?
- Is it observable?
- Is it falsifiable?
- Is it repeatable?
- Is it an inference, not a fact?
- What would disconfirm it?

Tag every output as one of:
	•	Fact
	•	Inference
	•	Hypothesis
	•	Narrative
	•	Strategy
