5. MVP workflow

Daily decision loop

1. Define objective
2. Build current state
3. Detect dominant signals
4. Route to one primary profile
5. Run 3 agents minimum:
   - Strategist
   - Goblin
   - Mirror
6. Choose one action
7. Log expected outcome
8. Execute
9. Review result within fixed time window
10. Update state and lessons

This is enough to make Pantheon a usable operating discipline immediately.

