8. Hard rules

Use these as repo doctrine:
	1.	No hidden state where possible
	2.	Every major claim gets a claim type
	3.	Every action gets an expected outcome
	4.	Every outcome gets a review
	5.	No canon without reality contact
	6.	Profiles shape behavior, not truth
	7.	Resource spend must be explicit
	8.	Mirror can veto
	9.	Goblin can block
	10.	Auditor warns; Strategist steers

