9. Clean README framing

Use this opening if you want:

Pantheon is a decision architecture for structured cognition under real constraints.
It combines explicit state, constraint profiles, specialized agents, resource-aware scoring, invariant checks, and feedback loops to improve decision quality over time.
It is not a mystical system, not a claim of hidden intelligence, and not a substitute for reality. It is a reproducible operating framework for thinking, choosing, testing, and learning.

